{
  "texts": [
    "Tarp (2023) lists the following types of functionalities found in writing assistants:",
    "(1) detection of problems in the written text (2) correction with suggestions for alternative solutions (3) prediction of word terminations and next words (4) transformation of syntax, style, sentences, etc.",
    "(5) translation with provision of L2 equivalents (6) consultation with look-ups in lexicographical databases.",
    "In Tarp's assessment, there was no writing assistant at the time of writing that would include all of these six functions.",
    "With generative AI at our disposal, it may be possible to delegate more of the task to a trained system."
  ]
}